parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Oil Sludge
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a knocking or clanking noise
the oil light flickers or stays on
the vehicle loses power
and smoke appears from the tailpipe.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: The vehicle overheats
the coolant leaks
and the engine makes a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a loud noise
the vehicle loses power
and the timing chain breaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels stiff or hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the power steering pump fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering system can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the steering wheel binds or catches when turning
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the rack and pinion steering system leaks fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the steering wheel binds or catches when turning
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the steering column fails to respond to input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, the horn to fail, and the cruise control to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the horn does not work
the cruise control does not engage
the radio controls do not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash
the airbag warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, and the airbags may not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag control module is broken.
